data.description: Seller says bring offer....This super cute home is bigger than she looks! You will be pleasantly surprised when you walk inside! Open floor plan that is perfect for entertaining...over 1900 sq feet on the upper level and a little over 700 sq feet of unfinished basement just waiting for your ideas! Master bedroom is a wonderful retreat with patio doors that lead to the wonderful oversized deck for hanging out and relaxing or for your entertaining needs! Kitchen has plenty of counterspace with gas stove that you will enjoy cooking on...along with stainless steel appliances...double driveway for your cars…and Circle drive could be added…washer dryer on main level and so much more! Come by and take a look you won't be disappointed.
